title: Player Attack S03E20 720p HDTV h264-Berg
description:
We're back! This week, Jonny Robot and Jessica Citizen pair up for a recap of the week that was E3 2015. If you missed any of the press conferences or big reveals, we've got you covered - from Bethesda's glorious Fallout 4 bonanza, Microsoft dabblings in augmented reality, EA's new best friend, and Ubisoft's three-way Tom Clancy faceoff - to Sony's fan-favourite trifecta, Nintendo's do-it-yourself Mario, Square Enix's new look at Hitman and the wonder that was the PC Gaming Show.

One week of solid gaming news, squished into one half-hour episode, including our picks for Game Of Show - you can't miss it! (...plus, of course, all the latest gaming news as well - this is Player Attack!)
